---
title: "US53 — Admin log in"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as System Administrator
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>LoginScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>Authenticate
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>Profile
  A->>B: enter email + password, tap LOG IN
  B->>C: signIn(email, password)
  C->>E: signInWithPassword(email, password)
  alt valid admin credentials
    E-->>C: AuthResponse (session)
    C->>E: fetchProfile(userId)
    E-->>C: Profile (role = admin)
    C-->>B: state = AsyncData (signed in)
    B-->>A: redirect to Admin portal (5-tab shell)
  else invalid credentials
    E-->>C: AuthException
    C-->>B: state = AsyncError
    B-->>A: "Incorrect email or password."
  end
  note over E: signInWithPassword via AuthGateway → Supabase Auth.<br/>fetchProfile via ProfileGateway → profiles (RLS)
